{"tid":163873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]雨天邊充電邊玩手機　湖南漢遭雷擊中亡","createTime":"2017-03-20T09:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T13:18:45.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e4719883905318daac6529d3c5538d6dc3b3766","tid":163873,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:56:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170320/bkncn-20170320155114082-0320_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170320%2Fbkncn-20170320155114082-0320_05011_001.html&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=852d4435\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170320/bkncn-20170320155114082-0320_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170320/photo/bkncn-20170320155114082-0320_05011_001_04b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170320%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170320155114082-0320_05011_001_04b.jpg&h=152fab75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手機竟成為引雷針？湖南婁底市20多歲的羅姓男子，昨晚在室內使用充電中的手機時，竟離奇被疑為手機引來的雷電擊中。其手上的手機更被當場擊碎，「碎片都找不到」。羅男經搶救後返魂乏術，而目睹兒子被雷擊一刻的羅母，事後痛哭不休，需由旁人扶起。<br />\n<br />\n事發昨晚8時許，新化縣正下着雷雨。羅男在家中一邊為手機充電，一邊玩手機，未料一聲響雷後，羅竟被一道雷電擊中。村支書聞訊後趕到現場報警求助，惟救護人員趕至現場急救時，羅男已經無生命迹象；經一系列心肺復甦搶救，羅男最終宣告不治。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2378c5656ef5956dd018789f492ba87458c26fbb","tid":163873,"uid":1088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:03:16.000Z","msg":"狂雷天威"},{"pid":"31f3e99f23e7b4882f4c7c1064c6d49b29fc25f5","tid":163873,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:05:19.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e543ba6e2ab011cd938e41c0cf1ea7d92f9590","tid":163873,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0